bug.short_desc: App not loading after get latest of master

long_desc.thetext:
Hi. I have just updated my qx framework to the current version of master.
My app has been working fine before, now it just shows a grey screen without throwing any error messages....
Help / Fix appreciated!!
Thanks!
Nik

SCSS did not work. As we announced you have to add input-active-border-color
Along with this feature we added a new SCSS theming variable to change the focused border color: $input-active-border-color
